ISLAMABAD, March 29 (APP): Minister for Kashmir Affairs, Gilgit Baltistan and States and Frontier Regions Engineer Amir Muqam on Saturday called on Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif and briefed him on the matters related to his ministry.
During the meeting, the overall national and political situation was also discussed, PM Office Media Wing said in a press release.
